Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:27.10,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}萬千思緒在赤紅烈焰中孕育強大勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.18,0:22:29.98,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}生生不息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:37.13,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}信任之心猶如無堅不摧之冰箭穿透一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:40.01,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}塵封於此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:42.76,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:45.33,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:48.25,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}面對不計其數的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:51.52,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}如若掉以輕心必將止步於此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:54.05,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}遙望雲天之上 浩瀚宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:56.50,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}任我獨步其中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:22:59.23,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}內心高雅之氣 高貴風範
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:01.63,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}令我心儀神往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:04.25,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}實現那天所描繪的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.43,0:23:09.57,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}和我們共同的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.64,0:23:14.48,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}邁向劍舞之祭壇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:19.35,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur4}踏上劍舞之舞台
